{"tid":2340690,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個以前鐘意過嘅女仔搵我影畢業相","createTime":"2020-12-25T16:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T17:07:18.000Z","uid":297738,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3c980c3dcbc087bff823f7499034f5922b710b","tid":2340690,"uid":297738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟啱啱postgrad畢業，以前讀bachelor嘅時候識左個同校女仔，但最後不了了之，然後大家嗰陣都搵到男女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n呢排同佢聯絡返，今日佢突然之間搵我影畢業相，話想我地兩個自己影，佢負責帶相機同腳架。不過以我所知佢宜家有男朋友，宜家應該點好，去嘅話好似唔係咁appropriate，定係純粹我諗多左？無乜經驗唔係好識拆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"7c8833bfb56ba58867ddadba911ce573465fb5c9","tid":2340690,"uid":78429,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"畢業相梗係同男朋友合照<br />\n合照嘅話梗係要搵人幫手影"},{"pid":"a5f33c03e910eaa2b35d12a999f2b4884ef831bd","tid":2340690,"uid":311268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"係啊 今次有機啦"},{"pid":"ced650d6936175f62832fd5f48834847f093beb1","tid":2340690,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"叫得 想去咪去咯<br />\n應該唔會比人拉入後巷掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314422989d8b3ed4d6d88f67097c5b8b888cc68e","tid":2340690,"uid":21355,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老味影張相都諗咁撚多嘢"},{"pid":"ed16c752be6766b9c735d9894e716537f686a0b2","tid":2340690,"uid":105924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"314422989d8b3ed4d6d88f67097c5b8b888cc68e","tid":2340690,"uid":21355,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"屌你老味影張相都諗咁撚多嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"X2 見相識一場先搵你影"},{"pid":"41a442a5f16e056867de12e790e714cdc601d647","tid":2340690,"uid":315852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"好似我之前咁，比中同約去集郵<img src=\"